videos.description: Notre Dame gets the steal, goes out running on the fastbreak and Steve Vasturia makes the layup.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense for Notre Dame

videos.description: Steve Vasturia gets the ball and makes the nice up-and-under move for the lay-in.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Vasturia with the nice up -and-under layup

videos.description: Boston College comes up with the steal and then A.J Turner finds Jerome Robinson for the dunk.
videos.headline: Boston College's Robinson with the powerful dunk

videos.description: Garland Owens makes the 3-pointer at the buzzer for Boston College.
videos.headline: Boston College's Owens drains 3-pointer as first half expires

videos.description: Boston College's Ky Bowman comes out of nowhere and gets the big block on Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Boston College's Bowman with the big block

videos.description: Notre Dame's Matt Farrell comes out running in transition and drains the deep 3-pointer to cut into Boston College's lead.
videos.headline: Fighting Irish's Farrell with the deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Off the miss 3-pointer by Matt Farrell, Bonzie Colson comes out of nowhere and finishes with the putback dunk for Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Colson with the nice putback dunk

videos.description: Matt Farrell draws two defenders and finds the cutting Bonzie Colson for the dunk.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Farrell gives a dime to Colson for the wide open dunk

videos.description: Breaking down Notre Dame 2nd half comeback in their 84-76 win over Boston College.
videos.headline: Breaking down the play of Notre Dame's big 4 in victory over Boston College
